                <div class="introblock"> <span class="manimg">
                <img width="45" height="50" src="http://voices.suntimes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/fitz-mug-newsroom.jpg" class="avatar avatar-50 photo wp-post-image" alt="" />				</span> 
                <span class="links links1 ">By <strong><a class="url fn n" href="http://voices.suntimes.com/author/lfitzpatrick/" title="View all posts by Lauren FitzPatrick" rel="author">Lauren FitzPatrick</a></strong> |  Get In Touch: <a href="https://twitter.com/bylaurenfitz" >@bylaurenfitz</a> | <a href="mailto: lfitzpatrick@suntimes.com" >lfitzpatrick@suntimes.com</a></span> <span class="links2">By <strong><a class="url fn n" href="http://voices.suntimes.com/author/lfitzpatrick/" title="View all posts by Lauren FitzPatrick" rel="author">Lauren FitzPatrick</a></strong></span>
         		<span class="poltics"><strong><a href="http://voices.suntimes.com/category/news/education-news/" title="View all posts in Education" rel="category tag">Education</a>, <a href="http://voices.suntimes.com/category/news/" title="View all posts in News" rel="category tag">News</a></strong>  - September 11, 2013 1:14 pm</span>									<h2>Update: First-grader&#8217;s hair gets caught in fan handed out by CPS</h2>
					<!-- GIGYA SHAREBAR TOP -->
					<div class="gigya-sharebar gigya-sharebar-top">
